      "writtenOn": "2019-08-01T20:46:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "OK, I can consolidate.\n\nThis will need to change with building different images for the different services, though, yes? As in, the image name will change but the handling for gcr_prefix, label, and commit tags will stay the same.",
